Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.47,Hamada,,0,0,0,,When we sit here together like this,it means {\i1}it {\i0}has started again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:09.15,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It seems the period for {\i1}it{\i0} has come around again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:09.15,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:13.15,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It seems to be of no advantage to us when we end up mixing with {\i1}that person{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:17.83,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Apparently he came just for this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.83,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Is that the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:21.17,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Whether he comes via shinkansen or planes, I'm not really sure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:22.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Just pay your own way here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:24.86,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If they paid their own way here, it would be acceptable
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:28.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,In fact, just don't come
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:28.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah, don't even come
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:42.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What, what, what
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a very slow revolution this time around
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who decided to make it turn anyways?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:49.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We don't know, probably someone from above
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever Hamada-san says, the programme will make arrangements for it so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:53.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,EH?! Was that how it goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:55.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We were waiting for it to turn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That is indeed the case
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this spring
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.37,0:00:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wednesday's Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,4th year running
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.01,0:01:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This episode, certain theories from past episodes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is what I have brought forth today
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Theory: Wednesday's Downtown quite often starts with a theory and ends with quite an unrelated turnabout
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:20.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:22.39,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah, that seems plausible
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:23.95,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It does happen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:27.17,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Like you run into something more interesting along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But as this show's main MCs
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, the orange resulting conclusion turns up doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning theory
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a gander from just that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was the two of you, you be able to tell which initial theory it was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:42.38,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Not so sure about that....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:45.75,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I would like to take a small objection about this..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.81,0:01:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:49.49,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You said Programme's MC but in actuality, I'm not really casted as one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, but Hamada-san is actually an MC though
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:56.06,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san should definitely know since he is the MC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:01:58.70,Hamada,,0,0,0,,But the main attention is normally over there where the panelists are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:02.03,Hamada,,0,0,0,,All I really do is scream "'kay 'kay"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:04.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Your job can't possibly be just to say "'kay 'kay"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:06.91,Hamada,,0,0,0,,"'kay 'kay, Take it away" is what I usually do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's begin the theory guessing quiz
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How well do you really remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How much of it do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go with this initial theory resolution
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I present to you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Conclusion: Kuro-chan is a liar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So what was the beginning theory to end like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:25.87,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Eh? The beginning theory was way different?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the beginning and the way it concludes is different
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.49,0:02:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is from when we first found out that Kuro-chan is a liar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.67,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Pigeons...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:33.17,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The one when we release the pigeons or something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:40.17,Hamada,,0,0,0,,And Kuro-chan has to make it all the way back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes, during that time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no, that's not correct
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:42.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The one where shit was stuck on him
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even close
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:46.83,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Eh? Wait, really? This is too hard
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:46.83,Hamada,,0,0,0,,If it continues like this, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a surprise prank
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was one of those Dokkiri-style theories Hamada-san loves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,During the viewing, Hamada-san was cackling away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:59.77,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,One of those 'XXX is the scariest' theories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,'XXX is the scariest after all', which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.63,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Most scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,In the house
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:09.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Theory: 'Returning to your home where there is a stranger waiting' is the most scariest theory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh, It's not that one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Can I bring up something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:16.02,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I have no recollection of it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:18.71,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hamada is absolutely no good
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.97,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He is not saying anything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even remember which possibilities to even guess
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:24.33,Hamada,,0,0,0,,When you guys were recollecting,nothing came up for me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.65,Hamada,,0,0,0,,'What are you guys talking about?' was what I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:29.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan is a liar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:33.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The beginning theory was:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:40.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Theory: 'When you awake and there's someone beside you' is the most scary theory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:50.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Whether the situation of 'When you awake and there's someone beside you' is really the scariest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:56.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In several comedians' homes, we planted a strange old man and waited for them to wake
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the most terrifying
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:05.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The last to be targeted was Kuro-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:04.20,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This guy again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.53,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.53,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be good
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:10.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While he is away , we have begun planting the hidden cameras
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:12.28,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They should be very well acquainted with this room already
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I am walkshing back to my home
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:19.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As always, Kuro-chan announces his activities on Twitter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:15.28,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,"Walkshing back"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:17.06,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,"Walkshing back"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:23.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In accordance to his actions, we are on standby
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:24.73,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,His alibi/whereabouts is SO out there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,From Shinjuku to my home is a bit far, I am going to do my best-shinyoo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.95,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What the heck is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.98,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's quite far
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:33.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From Shinjuku to Shinagawa, if one were to walk, it would take around 2 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:38.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It is time. The staff await outside for Kuro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:41.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After waiting around for 30 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.80,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's a taxi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.13,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:51.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A taxi has stopped in front of Kuro-chan's home
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:52.13,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:54.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just in case, the staff hide
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:58.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As it turns out, the one who stepped out of the taxi is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:03.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:02.60,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wa, scary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:03.83,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ah, so he lied
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:06.37,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What was that lie even for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:07.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A mystery remains as to why he needed to claim that he walked back home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:12.95,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The same goes for exposing his lie right now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:11.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We were close to running into him at his home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:17.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After he reached home, the tweet that he composed was
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.26,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's actually writing one
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, I will be reaching home.\NMy head is filled with the melody of Sarai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.85,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Whose sake is he even lying for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.31,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Scary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:26.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A Tweet formed by pretense and malice intent
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Our cameras have full footage of the entire on-goings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What a thing they have managed to capture
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:35.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And its now 1 am
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:33.86,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is awful
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:33.86,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,In a certain sort of way, he's amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.20,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They shot a completely different thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:42.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For some reason, he is going through his mail in full nude
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.86,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,No way!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.51,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Scary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:46.00,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Disgusting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:46.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next day he has work starting early in the morning yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:50.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He seems to have no intention of sleeping
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:52.43,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,In that case, just go outside and walk
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:53.75,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Chinsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:55.57,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Chinsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.97,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's eating chinsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:52.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And next,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,unexpectedly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:58.44,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,You going to eat?!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:02.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Chinsuko Squat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:02.73,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Whether he intents to lose or gain weight, its hard to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:04.42,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Chinsuko Squat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:09.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next, he raises his iron dumbbell up and..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.80,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,A selfie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.80,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's going to take a picture
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I can't sleep, I am doing muscle training-shin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But, the iron dumbbell is soon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.24,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:20.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,placed back into its initial position once the picture has been taken
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:20.41,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Just stop this already
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:22.41,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Just stop this trainwreck already
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:29.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At this point, he has finally made his last lying tweet of the day and heads towards slumber
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:33.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He goes to sleep with the lights and TV still on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:33.12,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The main act is from here onwards, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.68,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,From herein out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:35.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that being the case
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:40.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We were indeed distracted, finally we return to observe our theory
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:38.04,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ehhh.. he leaves his things like that before sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:41.18,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He did leave it in that messy state
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the end
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.27,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Scary, scary, this is going to be frightening
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.80,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's waking up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.32,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ah this is terrifying
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.40,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They finally met eye to eye
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Eh? Eh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:33.08,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That burping got to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:38.48,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Something weird came out of his mouth, how distasteful
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,About what exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh What is this precisely about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:50.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We have already grown accustomed to his reaction due to seeing it like 100 times
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:53.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We decided to ask about the other thing which really interested us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:55.32,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That was indeed tough
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.16,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Look at those eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We looked up your Twitter account and was piqued by
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned that you walked back home to your home from Shinjuku Station?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought up the fact that you were going back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't actually walk back, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:10.40,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Don't bring it up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, give me a moment, my piss is coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:14.36,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What did you mean you pissed yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't walk back home, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What do you mean? I totally walked back
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You returned via taxi, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:22.84,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's a bad face he's making right now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:24.72,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:24.72,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's definitely a villain's face
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me a second, erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We were watching
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:28.32,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Such things happen too
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a lie but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lies are too conspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mistaking me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a play,play wasn't the word I am looking for,how did I explain myself clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you at least acknowledge the fact that you did not walk back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by acknowledging the fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah I understand now, it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We have footage of you leaving the taxi anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:53.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So as it turns out, Kuro-chan is a liar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:58.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,By some mishap, we happen to chance upon Kuro-chan making up multiple lies on Twitter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The following series which features Kuro-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:04.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This was the origin and inspiration of it all
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go into the next question with enthusiasm
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, is this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It turned out to be a wig
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.51,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Eh, what's up with the ending
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be quite difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:19.77,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Wasn't this about the old guy being interviewed and the ..?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not concerning an old guy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:27.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The opener to this ending was:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:34.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Theory: Impossible to find a forehead that is narrower than Hirukawa's in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:41.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What we were looking for was a forehead shorter than 2.5 length to the eyebrows
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:45.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Does someone really exist which has a shorter forehead length?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:48.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the process of searching for someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:52.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We found someone in Osaka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm returning from work
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, returning from work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Near the end of May....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:07.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everywhere you look, hippopotamus teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:13.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A small-forehead woman has appeared, but is more than we hoped for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.37,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That is really something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:18.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which feature do people notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.51,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's one in a million
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you say your most distinguishing feature is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.31,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,For real
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to seem like a lame old person, so I try to stay hip
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to think we were asking about her outfit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for the narrowest forehead in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, I'll slide this back a little
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:43.77,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:43.77,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's sliding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.54,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wig. This is my real forehead, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:59.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was a wig
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:55.94,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's still halfway down though
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:58.48,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:01.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Continuing on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:05.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Chiba is getting some on the side
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:08.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The theory that gave birth to this somewhat different result
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:09.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:16.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Theory: "If you spilled tea at a Yazawa fan's house, they would never dry it with a Yazawa towel"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On this crazy Yazawa fan's way home
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:23.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We tried our experiment of intentionally spilling tea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:27.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And finally we interviewed him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My phone number is also Yazawa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take the last 4 numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"8-3-0" can be read as "ya-za-wa"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's fixated on 830
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But "8-7-4" is a more accurate number for the 50 year old fan*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy82\pos(380,53.333)\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&}*"8-7-4" can be read to sound like "has no teeth"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:42.86,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,So true
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.15,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:42.88,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's just
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:44.27,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What are you even saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:46.57,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's awful
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:51.34,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have any friends, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:53.54,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's so lame
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A Yazawa fan for 38 years
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:49.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A toothless man with loads of merchandise
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:52.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When we asked to take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually have another place
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the way
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:12:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just for your merchandise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.20,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's having a laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.30,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wow, amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just for merch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I rent it just for that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have other expenses?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I rent the room secretly
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for your wife to know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:16.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So, we went to the room secret even to his wife
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:15.22,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's like that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my other place
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:19.52,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we see inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Already you can get a feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.71,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right as you enter, even
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I made this actually.\NYou made this? \NYes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.19,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He made it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:33.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But before the Yazawa love can flow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:30.65,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's cute
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.05,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,So cute
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Chiba-san
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you messing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I just kinda stuck some stuff and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No that's not it, this is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No no no no no
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked guilty as hell saying that just now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:47.85,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not messing around, nope nope nope
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:50.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The confusion on his face is obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:54.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The marks of a woman are even more obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:55.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On top of that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got Snoopy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see that's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute. An awfully feminine design don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.43,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It could have been a present
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:04.03,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's bad news
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While we're on the topic
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:06.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That curtain earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.63,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.06,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can't possibly be homemade
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is seriously cool
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how much is the rent for this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,About 70,000 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not cheap
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:30.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is someone splitting the rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:30.62,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why would you ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:33.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And things like this were slipped in with the merch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiba-san, is this your handwriting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Yes this is my writing, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:44.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An itinerary for a live show at Budokan is written on the white board
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.17,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is too muc- huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:48.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But this handwriting is crazy suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:48.91,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's weird
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:53.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For some reason, even Christmas plans are included
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You really did right this, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you feeling when you drew this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's go to Budokan~♥"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write it now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird stroke order
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A super weird stroke order
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:09.29,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why is he writing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.29,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:10.90,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:13.02,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's like he's painting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:14.58,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the other half?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No good
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiba is getting some on the side
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That totally didn't match the theory
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:28.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That was exhausting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It really was exhausting, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving on, let's try to answer the question
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.85,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Our next theory
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't beat a demon without a pheasant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:39.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think I know this one
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:45.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Could Momotaro really rely
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Wait really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:50.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,On the dog, monkey, and pheasant to actually help?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're a little mixed up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:54.11,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Should I try saying that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, one more time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:57.85,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Once more- Hamada, you haven't said a damn thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:59.53,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:03.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I don't know a single one of these things
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You're always here, though
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:10.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You can't tame dogs, monkeys, or pheasants with dumplings
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First is the dog
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.52,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's taking it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:25.10,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Dogs are omnivorous, so it makes sense
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:21.80,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He ate it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:25.10,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:28.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He cautiously accepts the dumpling
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.74,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Where's he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:34.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But because it's hot, he takes it to the shade to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:38.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then, he somehow recruits a monkey
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want a dumpling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:47.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The pheasant won't be won over
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Momotaro, with just his dog and monkey, set out for the Island of Demons
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to defend the peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out, demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And then
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:13.88,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh it's Kukki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.89,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:19.72,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Scram
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:20.59,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Kuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.40,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.21,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The monkey ran away
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:31.27,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They just left him there
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,People with freaking Shonan license plates
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't going to impress no one in Yokohama
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:46.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He couldn't beat a demon without a pheasant
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:43.82,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What kind of ending is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:51.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Actually I was pretty close to the actual theory
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You were pretty close
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:54.13,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Isn't this guy the worst?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada, at least pay attention. Just focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What is going on with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:01.93,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well if you're sitting here thinking of things to say every time, you'll remember
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No no no no
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:04.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I'm always left over there, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:07.62,Hamada,,0,0,0,,All I ever do is say "Welcome!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Hamada
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound so proud to be completely neglecting your job
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:16.78,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What do you think you get paid for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:22.27,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Don't just repeat yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.82,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please teach me to negotiate a job
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:28.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Noooooo way
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:27.10,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's a sweet deal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pay attention, Hamada, just once
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:35.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Switching the entrance and exit theory, continued
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:40.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Theory: "The youngest and oldest are evenly matched"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:49.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This theory tests what happens when you pit the youngest and oldest athletes against each other in various events
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:53.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First up is Judo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:56.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Representing the oldest
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:02.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tadayuki Morimoto, 84 year old ranked 8-dan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:00.54,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:02.71,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:05.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Representing the youngest
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.57,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:11.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A 5 year old studying Judo in Kumakogen, Toki Sasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:17.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected, this is the ultimate age difference
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.64,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:22.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The match is beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:21.98,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ah it's starting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:23.81,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He doesn't look happy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:23.81,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He doesn't like this at all
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:27.05,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Does his tummy hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:27.05,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He doesn't feel good
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Does your tummy hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Young Toki is holding his stomach and leaving the ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.52,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Maybe he needs to pee?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:34.54,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:40.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Before the match can start, Toki leaves to go to his family
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.48,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:39.74,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:43.27,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,You're kidding
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He suddenly begins to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:49.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fighting an old man he doesn't know is scary
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.11,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's a stranger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:57.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At this point, Morimoto approaches the staff
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.99,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's so sad, though
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:55.41,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's going to talk to him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:58.57,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's describing it so dramatically
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because he's a stranger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, he's a 5 year old kid
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be making fun of his judo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing all of this to show on a variety show
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.26,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's pissed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what you're going for
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But this really goes against the spirit of judo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:09.71,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh he's super pissed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:12.32,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Fair enough
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:17.77,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:21.62,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't had any time to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've been doing this for 64 years
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Making a kid fight me after just 6 months is impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:25.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He got crazy angry with us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.08,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Obviously
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:30.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So this match ends with forfeit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:29.95,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh I see
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:34.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A few days later, we brought him back with a different opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:34.69,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wait, he's doing it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.32,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He came back
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.67,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:40.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time, the opponent is just old enough to compete nationally
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:40.19,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Way different
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:41.99,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is something
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:44.20,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:45.42,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:47.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kanagawa 5th grader Koshiro Sanada
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:49.07,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's much better qualified
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:52.47,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He should be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:52.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Morimoto shouldn't have any issues taking him on
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for calling you here a second time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you would, though
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.14,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He was really mad, though
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:56.71,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Well, he came didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I'll say about it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.58,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:03.58,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Really
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:05.72,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He'll have to retire
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Which basically means I'll lose
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:12.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At last the match starts
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:11.79,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I don't like this, regardless of what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:16.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Actually, Sanada-kun is a powerful figure getting 2nd place in the national tournament at age 11
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:23.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, Morimoto at 84 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:26.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,won his gold medal 8 times at the World Masters
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:29.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Who will win is totally unpredictable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:34.04,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Well, this kid seems pretty strong
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:34.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The match starts
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:38.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First, Sanada circles in from the right
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:38.08,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,There it is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There is a physical size difference,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:43.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but Sanada-kun is not shy of strength, even for adults
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:46.46,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is really like a normal match
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.59,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Good, good
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:54.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sanada, who has brought down 100 kg opponents at Nationals,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:55.47,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's pretty amazing then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:58.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,versus the 84-year old Masters gold medalist Morimoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.10,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.60,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:06.01,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Gramps, don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:06.01,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Keep it up, grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:08.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Morimoto who said he will not be thrown
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:08.31,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Gramps is getting tired
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:11.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This match may turn around at any second
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.18,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is really about stamina
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:14.12,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's staggering
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is an interesting matchup
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:16.19,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,If he gets thrown..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:18.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In terms of stamina, at 84 years old, Morimoto is at a considerable disadvantage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:18.56,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Thought so
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.66,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Doesn't have much strength
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:22.93,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Right, if it takes a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:24.09,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He can't do it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:27.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And afterwards, as the two fighters grapple
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:32.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the match shows some movement
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:38.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Morimoto falls! will he get pinned?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:41.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Sanada does the reverse scarf hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sanada, who was taken down
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:45.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Pins down his opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:48.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Morimoto is pinned!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:53.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Suddenly the oldest, Morimoto, has given up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:59.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With this, Sanada, the youngest, has won the match by ippon with a reverse scarf hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:00.56,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:03.30,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That was a great match
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:03.30,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That was really something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.33,0:22:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, it's not really about winning
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If the kid can make progress from here on out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,there's value in being present and competing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't matter whether I win or lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:21.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So, the result was "doesn't matter whether I win or lose"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:28.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And, there was one more judo plan with a different beginning and end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:35.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Theory: "Giant Shirota and Shinichi Shinohara are almost identical so they'll have a par match"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:38.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This match stems from just finding
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.70,0:22:42.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,their specialties based on similar appearances
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:47.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A memorable moment in our first mixed-rule showdown
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:52.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Competitive Eating Judo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:54.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The rules are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:23:01.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,1 minute and 30 seconds each of competitive eating and judo, 3 rounds each, for a total of 6 rounds
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:04.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The one with the most full points is the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:09.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,By the way, in judo ippon is 1 full point
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.33,0:23:14.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And in competitive eating, one makizushi roll will count as one full point
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:19.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In this match we can get an idea of their strength in their specialties
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:24.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At the end of round 2 there was only a gap of 1 point making it a tight game
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:31.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the last round begins with the competitive eating block, the opener to the judo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:31.76,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, this is not the time you want to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:33.22,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They really don't want to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:37.26,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh no, they're really thirsty too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:41.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will Shirota pull away again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:43.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will Shinohara be able to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:43.33,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They've become unable to eat huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:45.74,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Shirota really needs to make up the points
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.14,0:23:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:50.24,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Eat, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.77,0:23:52.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The referee prompts them once again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.17,0:23:52.71,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Shirota's not having anything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.91,0:23:54.01,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,You'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.71,0:23:55.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Barley tea in one hand, unable to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.01,0:23:57.11,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,If you don't eat you'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.65,0:23:57.11,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirota, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.45,0:24:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.52,0:24:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of out of breath
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,0:24:11.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Finally both fighters have reached for the makizushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:12.36,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It would be bad if he doesn't have at least one
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.86,0:24:15.23,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Since there's no way Shirota can get a point in judo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.90,0:24:16.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shirota crams down a makizushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.67,0:24:18.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He gets one makizushi down!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.64,0:24:21.07,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He needs to make it up here
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.64,0:24:24.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Uh oh, it seems like he's having difficulty swallowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.04,0:24:24.84,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It'd be funny if he got a point in judo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.87,0:24:26.11,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He needs a 5 point difference
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.04,0:24:28.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We've never seen Shirota like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.78,0:24:28.01,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.68,0:24:29.88,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,You won't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.28,0:24:32.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On the other hand Shinohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.65,0:24:34.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can't eat either!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.25,0:24:38.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In this one-and-a-half minute round, each of them
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.96,0:24:43.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,have a normal meal of 2 and 1 makizushi respectively
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.03,0:24:45.96,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's a normal meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.03,0:24:48.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and the final eating round ends
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.03,0:24:48.43,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is not good
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.00,0:24:48.43,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Just two!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.43,0:24:52.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their point difference is two. Can Shirota make a clean break?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.44,0:24:55.31,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Shinohara's stamina has run out
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.87,0:24:56.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the last duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.54,0:24:58.21,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Shirota, go get him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.91,0:25:00.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shinohara didn't do anything but he got a full point!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.84,0:25:02.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A very important point!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.15,0:25:06.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The rest is abysmal. Shirota has 1 min 20 sec
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.65,0:25:04.48,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.58,0:25:08.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Another point!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.75,0:25:09.79,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,one minute left!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.55,0:25:14.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With no other choice, Shirota has to win this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.12,0:25:12.02,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.95,0:25:13.06,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,You can do it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.06,0:25:14.89,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Come on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.56,0:25:18.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He drags around!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.63,0:25:20.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.33,0:25:24.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shinohara wins this showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.60,0:25:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.14,0:25:32.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Therefore, "One can't eat right after exercising"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.01,0:25:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.04,0:25:35.35,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There's more!?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.35,0:25:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna keep going
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.08,0:25:36.98,Hamada,,0,0,0,,This is plenty enough
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.98,0:25:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.55,0:25:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your job
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.65,0:25:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"It turned into an uncharacteristically wholesome plan"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.12,0:25:45.96,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What is this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.96,0:25:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's pretty hard
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.66,0:25:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not ringing any bells?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.19,0:25:53.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This program
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.99,0:25:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.16,0:25:57.03,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,doesn't ever get wholesome
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.53,0:25:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It does, here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.03,0:25:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.07,0:26:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Theory: "Professionals impersonating teachers will have students die of laughter!"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.87,0:26:04.11,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh, this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.21,0:26:07.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This was a good plan
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.54,0:26:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.71,0:26:12.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This theory turned unintentionally heartful:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.08,0:26:14.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The setting was:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.95,0:26:18.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fuji Gakuen Middle School in Yamanashi prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.79,0:26:25.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And these are the pros in charge of the teachers impressions!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.76,0:26:25.76,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That lineup is surely something!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.26,0:26:34.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The pros visited the school in order to gather information about the teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.47,0:26:41.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First, when inquiring some of the school alumni:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.94,0:26:41.98,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh I see
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.28,0:26:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this teacher, called Oomori sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.12,0:26:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.18,0:26:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Science
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.12,0:26:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When he gets mad, he gets like super agitated
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.42,0:26:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,An goes like this
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.86,0:26:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All they way up, suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.16,0:26:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. His intonation too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.93,0:27:00.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next, the pros will watch the lessons live
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.46,0:27:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you understand that "other" is singular, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.83,0:27:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She raises her tone at the end like "NE"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.17,0:27:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She talks quickly, and then "NE"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.04,0:27:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As if she were following a rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.21,0:27:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, like this
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.01,0:27:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at the chalk
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.38,0:27:18.78,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This can be funny
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.08,0:27:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be possible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.32,0:27:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.38,0:27:21.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.52,0:27:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.15,0:27:24.05,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,So, the teachers came too
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.79,0:27:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.16,0:27:31.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The pros will meet the teachers firsthand
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.33,0:27:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oota sensei, you seem like a very serious teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.53,0:27:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you ever laugh out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.47,0:27:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.94,0:27:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the funniest thing you last at recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.81,0:27:54.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Well, after gathering gathering info about the teachers, we head back to TBS
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.55,0:28:02.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are joined by the two that were unavailable, and discuss
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.29,0:28:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.13,0:28:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we decide who is going to wear a disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.60,0:28:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see first... who can get the main roles
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.80,0:28:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.07,0:28:15.14,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That looks so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.71,0:28:21.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Depending on the looks, voice tone and such, each pro was assigned a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.25,0:28:28.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kannatsuki will impersonate the eccentric Yamaguchi sensei, ex- member of a "poop seminar"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.69,0:28:34.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Also, "bad diction" Oomori sensei, will be impersonated by Hori
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.29,0:28:41.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mikan will impersonate Ebara sensei, who can't stop saying "Who can try?"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.00,0:28:47.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The serious but also good at dancing Oota sensei will be impersonated by Ehara
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.67,0:28:55.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Mirakuru will be in charge of Nakayama sensei, who hisses after finishing her sentences
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.41,0:29:05.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Denture" Kanekatsu sensei and "Bald gag" Okuwaki sensei will also appear during the show
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.89,0:29:05.49,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Looks like a medley
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.29,0:29:08.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How did it turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.86,0:29:18.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The clueless students are gathered in the multi-purpose hall
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.07,0:29:19.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.07,0:29:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,These days you've all been slacking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.44,0:29:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why you're all here
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.21,0:29:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a teacher that has something to say to all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.95,0:29:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Us teachers have been holding back!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.11,0:29:38.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The students, after being fooled to believe they were being scolded, will meet the impersonators!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.79,0:29:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Every teacher is each
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.99,0:29:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,going to have a few words
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.69,0:29:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,with all of you here
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.97,0:29:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.80,0:29:58.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After the unexpected appearance, they still don't know what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.87,0:30:00.04,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It was like: "what's going on?"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.88,0:30:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, this guy looks a lot like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.38,0:30:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.45,0:30:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, who are YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.38,0:30:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yamaguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.38,0:30:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I AM Yamaguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.28,0:30:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'M YAMAGUCHI
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.45,0:30:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yamaguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.05,0:30:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really are Yamaguchi, tell me. You were in a seminar back in college, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.12,0:30:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Which seminar?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.26,0:30:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Turd seminar
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.72,0:30:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A turd seminar!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.03,0:30:18.50,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're laughing a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.90,0:30:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Yamaguchi has eaten bugs right? Which insect did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.80,0:30:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A stink bug
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.30,0:30:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A stink bug!!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.70,0:30:28.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After realizing what's going on... they burst out laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.51,0:30:30.44,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They find it hilarious
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.27,0:30:30.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.64,0:30:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many other teachers that are also angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.61,0:30:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oomori sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.79,0:30:44.92,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The resemblance is amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.79,0:30:46.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They achieved an amazing resemblance
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.49,0:30:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.76,0:30:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the pinky, sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.33,0:30:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I want you to remember the important things needed for a flower to blossom
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.10,0:30:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one, two and three of them
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.90,0:31:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sensei, that's weird... It's pretty strange
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.71,0:31:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stamen and pistil... Please remember that...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.55,0:31:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.85,0:31:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that, I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.88,0:31:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can remember it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.68,0:31:15.65,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They find it hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.69,0:31:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.62,0:31:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You all...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.72,0:31:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your diction is terrible, so we have no idea what you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.52,0:31:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My dihsshion?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.36,0:31:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no idea what you say when you get mad
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.63,0:31:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a teacher with a better diction in this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.57,0:31:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,WOW, WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.80,0:31:35.41,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're going "WOW"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.11,0:31:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.24,0:31:40.88,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They really look alike
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.21,0:31:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So the other day we left it at page twentyfiiiiiiive
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.98,0:31:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We will continuuuuue...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.89,0:31:53.52,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're laughing like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.92,0:31:54.59,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They really are
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.42,0:31:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a one line joke
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.56,0:31:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When comparing "the other"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.26,0:31:58.86,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're laughing their heads off
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.10,0:32:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When comparing "the other" to..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.17,0:32:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,... "the othersssh"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.57,0:32:08.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.61,0:32:14.04,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.74,0:32:19.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They started laughing right after the entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.48,0:32:22.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What about the real person?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.02,0:32:29.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In spite of the circumstances, he remains expressionless
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.16,0:32:30.86,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.89,0:32:32.63,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's never laughed in his life
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.63,0:32:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.34,0:32:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with your right hand, sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.81,0:32:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.45,0:32:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And your mouth? That's a duck face
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.08,0:32:53.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The contrast is hilarious
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.82,0:32:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dance now
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.09,0:33:04.06,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Apparently he dances for the school festival
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.49,0:33:04.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the last one to make entrance is...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.83,0:33:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're really similar
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.67,0:33:13.10,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.14,0:33:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'd like to talk about my favourite team: Nippon Ham
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.21,0:33:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ssss...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.72,0:33:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dot, dot...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.82,0:33:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of dots!! Too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.49,0:33:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dot dot dotdotdotdot...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.86,0:33:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ssssss
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.80,0:33:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's saying it right...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.30,0:33:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we have Okuwaki sensei say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.04,0:33:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Baldiewaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.35,0:34:00.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And finally they will go for Kanekatsu sensei's motto: "Nice, nice!"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.48,0:34:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about the whole show?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.89,0:34:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was... "nice, nice"!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.39,0:34:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nice, nice!"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.06,0:34:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm better at nicenicing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.63,0:34:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious I'm better!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.73,0:34:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I AM BETTER
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.70,0:34:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm "nice,nice"!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.47,0:34:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone should decide who's the "nice, nicest"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.27,0:34:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, come here
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.31,0:34:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, how was our impersonations?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.61,0:34:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nice, nice"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.98,0:34:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.39,0:34:42.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And like that, the impersonation show achieves a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.46,0:34:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you surprised at the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.93,0:34:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You might've thought "What's going on?" or something
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.18,0:34:48.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.37,0:34:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.94,0:34:54.54,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're dying from laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.31,0:34:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.55,0:34:58.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They're literally dying from laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.42,0:35:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.55,0:35:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because you're happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.32,0:35:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why??
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.16,0:35:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.66,0:35:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that you are overflowed with joy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.53,0:35:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's just overflowed with joy
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.38,0:35:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel like really we accomplished?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.78,0:35:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I really do
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.28,0:35:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,First time feeling like this
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.01,0:35:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The best in 10 years
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.85,0:35:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we did really well
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.52,0:35:25.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Students
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.85,0:35:26.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.05,0:35:28.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And also
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.46,0:35:30.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The impersonators
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.52,0:35:33.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone was filled with joy and laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.46,0:35:36.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It surely was a great day
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.53,0:35:42.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In a few words: it was an unexpectedly a heart-warming show
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.94,0:35:45.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next up,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.02,0:35:49.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"There are some weirdos in this world"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.53,0:35:53.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which theory was the entry for this verification result?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.14,0:35:59.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,People that get "Japanese style toilets" installed in a new construction is seriously next to 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.52,0:36:07.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So we did a survey amongs contractors that do toilet installation around the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.13,0:36:12.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We discovered a newly built home with a Japanese style toilet in Nara Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.09,0:36:12.55,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's in Kansai!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.32,0:36:18.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This surely looks like a home that fancies the "Japanese style"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.38,0:36:16.92,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Yeah pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.52,0:36:19.32,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.28,0:36:25.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Could they really have installed a Japanese style toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.80,0:36:23.58,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Definitely new!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.80,0:36:23.58,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.58,0:36:26.22,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.58,0:36:26.22,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Newly built too
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.02,0:36:27.08,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.26,0:36:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're with TBS Television.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.25,0:36:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.22,0:36:32.18,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,"Please come in"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.25,0:36:34.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The husband didn't want to show their face on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.05,0:36:34.86,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Didn't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.86,0:36:38.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We're immediately shown to the toilet in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.86,0:36:41.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fscx45\fscy72\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\pos(310,53.333)}TN: The sticker on his face says "Japanese Style".
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.52,0:36:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.25,0:36:40.01,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.60,0:36:40.33,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is not good
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.72,0:36:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,On the second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.33,0:36:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.40,0:36:43.10,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is a nice house.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.10,0:36:46.70,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wow it's really Western-style!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.02,0:36:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.70,0:36:49.02,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,No way! It's a Western-style door!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.02,0:36:52.72,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Tamura, ya fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.82,0:36:52.72,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,NO WAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.72,0:36:54.46,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,WOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.34,0:36:55.74,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,WHY!?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.46,0:36:56.89,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's sparkling!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.74,0:36:58.73,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's really pretty too!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.89,0:36:58.73,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.14,0:36:55.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They had one...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.58,0:36:59.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A super pretty Japanese style toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.73,0:37:00.57,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.23,0:37:01.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.88,0:37:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Still brand new!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.54,0:37:07.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, why do they have one in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.90,0:37:05.88,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's special
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.37,0:37:07.10,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.88,0:37:08.28,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.10,0:37:11.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's for a very surprising reason
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.28,0:37:11.19,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They even have a freaking outlet in the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.19,0:37:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So why did you get a Japanese style toilet installed?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.68,0:37:15.56,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The hell does it say "Japanese style" on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.22,0:37:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I have a son that's gonna be in high school
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.16,0:37:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and he really insisted on getting one installed
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.40,0:37:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My son yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.40,0:37:22.40,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.40,0:37:24.25,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Like a manic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.78,0:37:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the point of, if we don't get one I'm out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.58,0:37:29.62,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What a strange guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.88,0:37:30.69,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.69,0:37:32.60,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.42,0:37:34.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Somehow, the "tradition" was strongly demanded by their high school son.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.33,0:37:35.09,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.20,0:37:36.42,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is a real plot twist
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.20,0:37:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.60,0:37:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come down for a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.14,0:37:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So the son's face is good to show huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.05,0:37:49.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their son. Yuuki, 15 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.05,0:37:46.22,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Hunk
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.86,0:37:48.92,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.72,0:37:49.71,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.71,0:37:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be Japanese style?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.69,0:37:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well uh, there's always been one in the house since I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.30,0:38:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got so used to it that I can't use a western one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.85,0:38:02.45,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,You gotta try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.26,0:38:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You had one in the previous house?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.46,0:38:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.49,0:38:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it cause a lot of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.09,0:38:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there aren't any if I go outside
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.50,0:38:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If I got to like department stores
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.78,0:38:11.33,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.40,0:38:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So in times like that, it's kind of bothersome
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.27,0:38:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.86,0:38:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hold it in... earnestly
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.72,0:38:18.60,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That can't be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.74,0:38:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When was the last time you went on a western style toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.38,0:38:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder. I just can't remember any time
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.85,0:38:32.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We are used to the fact that, if a western one isn't available we go to the traditional one
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.94,0:38:32.45,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.45,0:38:37.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But for Yuuki, it's a firm rejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.49,0:38:37.54,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's opposite
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.54,0:38:38.98,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What's bad about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.39,0:38:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the family use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.80,0:38:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No one but myself no.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.27,0:38:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's only for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.24,0:38:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.04,0:38:46.82,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They have another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.29,0:38:48.37,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's downstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.65,0:38:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only {\i1}my{\i0} room
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.04,0:38:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever used a washlet?*
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.04,0:38:57.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fscx52\fscy73\pos(340,53.333)\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&}*TN: An electronic toilet seat with bidet functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.34,0:38:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.73,0:38:55.25,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,You gotta try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.26,0:38:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we have you try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.01,0:38:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, only one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.54,0:39:03.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so, he enters the family toilet for the very first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.70,0:39:06.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His first wash toilet experience in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.93,0:39:09.33,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,No, he's got to have done this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.82,0:39:10.85,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He has!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.89,0:39:12.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sure enough
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.70,0:39:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx133\fscy158}AGH!*
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.70,0:39:31.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fscx46\fscy72\pos(664,53.333)\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&}*TN: On wash toilets like these there's a bidet function that sprays water from a retracting arm inside the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.47,0:39:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just harsh
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.84,0:39:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx133\fscy158}OOGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.05,0:39:25.73,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Stop pulling my leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.89,0:39:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx133\fscy158}Ouch ouch ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.33,0:39:28.96,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Cause it's his first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.96,0:39:30.56,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He said "ouch".
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.61,0:39:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.08,0:39:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Unpleasant
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.09,0:39:34.45,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Be careful with the pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.36,0:39:40.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In conclusion, "There are some weirdos in this world"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.45,0:39:37.45,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Gotta lower the pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.18,0:39:42.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next up,
