Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.29,0:40:12.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which theory was the entry for this verification result?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.64,0:40:18.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Theory: Hiroshi Itsuki has a strong grip
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.24,0:40:18.44,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What kind of theory is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.44,0:40:19.34,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is just messing around
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.44,0:40:23.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Enka singer Itsuki Hiroshi, gripping his fists for 45 years
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.29,0:40:27.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Could his grip be stronger than the average male of the same age?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.29,0:40:27.50,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is not what it's about
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.50,0:40:29.26,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.84,0:40:32.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But when we requested the person apperance
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.26,0:40:32.36,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Right, they asked him
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.36,0:40:35.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,they naturally refused
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.73,0:40:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.17,0:40:43.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A Hiroshi Itsuki look-alike
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.17,0:40:46.09,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's so unrelated
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.13,0:40:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you been impersonating Hiroshi Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.84,0:40:48.49,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He does it well though
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.72,0:40:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,31 years this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.86,0:40:52.46,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.61,0:40:53.56,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's long for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.06,0:40:55.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's been holding his fist for 31 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.18,0:41:03.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Does Itsuki Hiroshi's grip strength exceed 39.7 kg that of an ordinary male in their 60s?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.37,0:41:04.77,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Does he have to karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.25,0:41:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ Yokohama Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.86,0:41:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ In a small room in a hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.32,0:41:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ The lingering scent of the kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.20,0:41:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ was the smoke of cigarettes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.94,0:41:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ Blues
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.37,0:41:34.42,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Not yet
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.94,0:41:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ Whistle
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.68,0:41:36.42,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.70,0:41:37.70,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's reaching the top now
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.77,0:41:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ A woman's tears
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.14,0:41:42.64,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.49,0:41:43.22,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.22,0:41:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ That person went and gone
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.10,0:41:45.97,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh he did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.81,0:41:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ That person went and gone
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.02,0:41:53.57,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't be holding it up like that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.13,0:41:53.57,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,right
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.02,0:41:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,♫ I'm not coming home anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.56,0:42:02.70,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's really into it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.23,0:42:06.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What about his grip strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.09,0:42:07.65,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They made us listen quite a lot of that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.33,0:42:12.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was 41kg
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.96,0:42:12.66,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.66,0:42:14.63,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's over 39.7kg
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.63,0:42:23.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He slightly exceeded the average grip strength of an ordinary male in their 60s
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.99,0:42:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, Itsuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.09,0:42:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grip strength is stronger than average
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.30,0:42:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.81,0:42:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.39,0:42:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The average grip strength of someone in their 60s is 39.7kg
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.70,0:42:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I just turned 56 years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.24,0:42:40.02,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.02,0:42:46.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,By the way, the average grip strength of men in their 50s is 46kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.26,0:42:46.38,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.86,0:42:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Onto the next one, the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.24,0:42:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.53,0:42:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"The result left a bad aftertaste"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.45,0:42:55.89,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\fscx98\fscy127}THAT'S ALL OF THEM!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.78,0:42:55.89,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\fscx98\fscy127}THAT HAPPENS ALL THE TIME!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.89,0:42:57.39,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's on all of them, all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.39,0:43:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, not all of them
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.06,0:43:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not all of them are like this
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.68,0:43:04.94,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Today too!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.94,0:43:06.91,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Now too
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.80,0:43:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.91,0:43:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a bad aftertaste now?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.94,0:43:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the one:
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.45,0:43:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A crime scene psychic can tell what happened just by entering a room
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.11,0:43:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This was uh, miles away
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.11,0:43:22.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Right right
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.46,0:43:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the end, the psychic
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.93,0:43:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,was like "The spirits are angry"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.29,0:43:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"I don't know anything, but I know that"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.59,0:43:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I got all 3 items flawlessly wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.73,0:43:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't catch them at all
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.33,0:43:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of how variety shows are planned out
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.16,0:43:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I had times were I thought "I wonder how this will go".
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.90,0:43:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I'm sensing that the deceased are angry
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.08,0:43:57.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And with that, the result left a bad aftertaste
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.12,0:43:57.98,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What the hell!?
